      </strong>
      NordVPN offers a unique feature that routes your connection through two servers for added security.
     </li>
<li>
<strong>
       Large Server Network:
      </strong>
      It has over 5,400 servers in 60 countries, ensuring a reliable connection.
     </li>
<li>
<strong>
